{"text_id":118151,"tokens":["Vor","tices"," in"," Bose","-","Einstein"," Condens","ates",":"," Theory"," abstract",":"," As"," the"," pioneers"," of"," this"," research",","," we"," have"," investigated"," the"," theoretical"," properties"," of"," vortices"," in"," Bose","-","Einstein"," condens","ates"," (","BEC","s",")."," Our"," primary"," goal"," is"," to"," shed"," light"," on"," the"," intricate"," dynamics"," of"," these"," quantum"," entities",","," which"," play"," a"," crucial"," role"," in"," a"," wide"," range"," of"," phenomena",","," from"," quantum"," turbulence"," to"," topological"," defects","."," To"," achieve"," this",","," we"," employ"," a"," combination"," of"," analytical"," and"," numerical"," techniques",","," focusing"," on"," the"," Gross","-","P","ita","ev","ski","i"," equation"," (","G","PE",")"," and"," the"," Landau","-","Lif","sh","itz"," equation"," (","LLE",")"," as"," prime"," tools","."," Our"," results"," indicate"," that"," vortices"," in"," BEC","s"," exhibit"," unique"," properties",","," such"," as"," quanti","zed"," circulation"," and"," topological"," stability",","," which"," are"," distinct"," from"," those"," observed"," in"," classical"," systems","."," We"," also"," find"," that"," the"," interplay"," between"," the"," vortex"," core"," size"," and"," the"," condensate","'","s"," density"," exhibits"," a"," nontrivial"," dependence"," on"," the"," system","'","s"," parameters","."," Furthermore",","," our"," calculations"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," vortex"," dynamics"," can"," be"," influenced"," by"," the"," presence"," of"," an"," external"," magnetic"," field"," and"," non","uniform"," trapping"," potential","."," This"," research"," is"," motivated"," by"," the"," quest"," to"," understand"," the"," fundamental"," physics"," governing"," BEC","s"," and"," their"," potential"," applications"," in"," quantum"," technology","."," Our"," findings"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," into"," the"," behavior"," of